texts.label: text
texts.orig: This document provides the non-proprietary security policy for the XYZ Cryptographic Module v1.0. The module implements FIPS 140-3 approved cryptographic algorithms and is designed for use in secure communication applications.
texts.text: This document provides the non-proprietary security policy for the XYZ Cryptographic Module v1.0. The module implements FIPS 140-3 approved cryptographic algorithms and is designed for use in secure communication applications.

texts.label: text
texts.orig: The module meets FIPS 140-3 Level 2 requirements for all security areas except physical security, which meets Level 1 requirements.
texts.text: The module meets FIPS 140-3 Level 2 requirements for all security areas except physical security, which meets Level 1 requirements.

texts.label: text
texts.orig: The XYZ Cryptographic Module is a software-based cryptographic module that provides cryptographic services to applications. The module is implemented as a dynamic library that can be integrated into various software applications.
texts.text: The XYZ Cryptographic Module is a software-based cryptographic module that provides cryptographic services to applications. The module is implemented as a dynamic library that can be integrated into various software applications.
